@node intro "Introduction"

	@{b}What is it?@{ub}
Black is a simple fractal generator. Black lets you zoom around in a preview window, and can save black and white iff pictures to disk. Black can render pictures of almost any size.

	@{b}Who, How@{ub}
Black is written by @{"Albert Bertilsson" link me}, in C.
@endnode


@node install "Installation"

	@{b}Installation@{ub}
This is the easiest part, since you are reading this document you have successfully unpacked the archive, all you have to do is to copy Black to the place you prefer.
@endnode


