@node req "Requirements"

	@{b}Requirements@{ub}
Black requires a 020+ processor. @{"I" link me} made it this way because most users have a 020+.
A 68881 coprocessor is recommended.

Black probably needs OS 3.0, @{"I" link me} have nothing but mine and a friends machine to test Black on, and these are both OS 3.0.

Oh, some libraries to;
	dos
	exec
	gadtools
	graphics
	icon
	intuition
	reqtools
@endnode


@node future "Future and History"

	@{b}Future plans@{ub}
Since @{"I" link me} do my military service now, there won't be a lot of enhancements made to this software in the near future. If @{"I" link me} get a lot of response from you, @{"I" link me} might consider to continue development. If you have any problems, or find any bugs, write to @{"me" link me}, and @{"I" link me} will try to correct it.

	@{b}History@{ub}

	Black 1.2
		Speeded up rendering.
		Changed the rendering of icons, they look nicer now.
		Changed this guide, since new amigaguide readers would not read the old one correctly.
		Optimized code a bit.

	Black 1.0
		Initial release.
@endnode


